metadata.name: Matrix
metadata.description:
Intriguing, atmospheric and dynamic...
I only look like a cold-blooded killer, but I have a great love in my heart that can completely turn the world upside down.
Strong, confident, self-sufficient...I always come to the rescue, even if it might cost me my life. I have my own vision and boundaries and I act according to my principles. 

Trinity is one the most important character in “The Matrix”, without which all philosophy would collapse.
